{"arkId":"cl010120585","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010120585","modified ":"2026-01-14","title":"Panneau de la guerre","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"incrustation de meuble"},{"type":"Titre","value":"Panneau de la guerre"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : Dynastique archa\u00efque IIIB (Vers 2500-2400 av. J. - C.) (-2500 - -2340)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-2500,"endYear":-2340,"imprecision":"","text":"Dynastique archa\u00efque IIIB","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"AO 17572","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"},{"value":"AO 19820","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"sc\u00e8ne de guerre (prisonnier, guerrier, dignitaire, enseigne : taureau, char, casque, kaunak\u00e8s, robe, arme)\r\n\r\nEtat de l\u0027oeuvre : incomplet\r\nPr\u00e9cision sur l\u0027objet : Reconstitution d\u0027A. Parrot d\u00e9mont\u00e9e en 2013 pour \u00eatre pr\u00e9sent\u00e9e en 3 panneaux : un dit \u0022des dignitaires\u0022, un dit \u0022des prisonniers\u0022 et un dit du \u0022char\u0022. \r\nFrise d\u0027un panneau d\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9ments d\u0027incrustation montrant un d\u00e9fil\u00e9 sur deux registres de divers personnages. Tentative de reconstitution d\u0027une sc\u00e8ne de victoire : une file de dignitaires portant calotte, herminette et kaunak\u00e8s se dirige vers la gauche, pr\u00e9c\u00e9d\u00e9e d\u0027un porte-enseigne et suivie de prisonniers nus et ligot\u00e9s ; une file de guerriers marchant vers la droite va \u00e0 leur rencontre.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":"","shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : coquillage = coquille (nacr\u00e9e), pl\u00e2tre\r\nMat\u00e9riau secondaire : pierre (rouge), bitume\r\nTechnique : incrust\u00e9, incis\u00e9 (d\u00e9cor)","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"Premi\u00e8re mission : 1933-34 pour tous les num\u00e9ros M. entre M. 158 et M. 474","placeOfDiscovery":"Mari temple d\u0027Ishtar cour 20 (sur le dallage)","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Parrot, Andr\u00e9","note":" (mission 1933-34)","role":", Fouilleur\/Arch\u00e9ologue"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"partage apr\u00e8s fouilles","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s orientales","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"partage apr\u00e8s fouilles"}],"denomination":[{"value":"incrustation de meuble"}],"material":[{"value":"coquillage = coquille"},{"value":"pl\u00e2tre"},{"value":"bitume"},{"value":"pierre"}],"technic":[{"value":"incis\u00e9"},{"value":"incrust\u00e9"}],"description":[{"value":"taureau"},{"value":"prisonnier"},{"value":"guerrier"},{"value":"dignitaire"},{"value":"sc\u00e8ne de guerre"},{"value":"kaunak\u00e8s"},{"value":"robe"},{"value":"arme"},{"value":"casque"},{"value":"char"},{"value":"enseigne"}],"place":[{"value":"Mari temple d\u0027Ishtar cour 20"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Poinsot, Delphine ; Spruyt, Margaux ; Moreau, Kilian (dir.), Equid\u00e9s, le cheval, l\u0027\u00e2ne et la mule dans les empires de l\u0027Orient ancien, Actes du colloque international tenu \u00e0 l\u0027INHA et au Domaine de Chantilly les 12 et 13 octobre 2018, Routes de l\u0027Orient Actes III, Paris, Routes de l\u0027Orient, 2022","bibliographyDate":"2022","bibliographyDetail":"p. 78, n\u00b0 78(d)","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Couturaud, Barbara, Les incrustations en coquille de Mari, Turnhout, Brepols, 2019","bibliographyDate":"2019"